::Spears::

She looked at Striker, "You killed the arim chairs with finess and 
style.  It'll take me a while to get that good, but I shall try." she 
said trying not to laugh too hard.

She knew why he did it, to save what little pride she had left.
She walked up to him and kissed him on the cheek.  
"Thanks for saving me from the killer chairs."  She turned and walked 
a little faster towards the ark with a big grin on her face.
